Portuguese Allspice

5 tbsp sweet paprika
1 tsp freshly ground black peper
1 tsp chile powder
1 tsp ground cumin
1 tsp ground cinnamon
1 tsp freshly grated nutmeg
1 tsp ground allspice
1 tsp dried oregano
1 tsp ground ginger
1 tsp ground clove
1 bay leaf, crushed with morta and pestle
1 tsp dried lemon zest (1/2 lemon)
1 tsp orange zest (1/3 orange)

Combine all dry ingredients ingredients. Zest the lemon and orange over the mix and stir to combine. Can store covered in refrigerator for up to 1 week.

